Enum EntityColumnPrefix

    Serializable, Comparable<EntityColumnPrefix>, ColumnPrefix<EntityTable>

    public enum EntityColumnPrefix
extends Enum<EntityColumnPrefix>
implements ColumnPrefix<EntityTable>
    Identifies partially qualified columns for the entity table.
